text: Phillips Flying Ranch Airport is a public airport located fifteen miles (24.1 km) southeast of the central business district (CBD) of Rockwall, in Rockwall County, Texas, United States. The airport itself is located in Hunt County The airport is used solely for general aviation purposes. == Facilities == Phillips Flying Ranch Airport has one runway: * Runway 13/31: 3,344 x 50 ft.
